snippet.title: DarkwebStreamer - Official Trailer | The MIX x Kinda Funny Spring Showcase 2024
snippet.description:
Take another look at DarkwebSTREAMER in this unsettling trailer for the upcoming horror RPG sim. 
Become an occult streamer on a 90s dark internet. Experience a fully procedurally generated world and endless sinister stories as you grow your stream, surf the web, perform rituals, make hard choices, manage your stats, and try to survive your increasingly haunted apartment. DarkwebSTREAMER is coming to PC.
